; fill: currentColor; font-size: 15px;\" transform=\"translate(0,-12)\">y</text></g><path d=\"M0,155.664L311.322,155.664L311.328,0L0,0L0,155.664\" fill=\"#B7B7B7\" style=\"mix-blend-mode: multiply;\"></path><text x=\"155.6640625\" y=\"59.094690393518505\" dx=\"-13.25px\" dy=\"13.5px\" fill=\"currentColor\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-style: italic; font-family: Noto Serif;\">O</text><path d=\"M0,155.664L311.322,155.664\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3px\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"7,3\"></path></g></svg><div role=\"region\" aria-label=\"Long description for graph of an inequality\" class=\"sr-only\"><ul><li>The boundary of the inequality is a dashed line.<br/>\n<ul>\n<li>The line is horizontal.</li>\n<li>The line passes through the following points:<br/>\n<ul>\n<li>(negative 3 comma negative 4)</li>\n<li>(0 comma negative 4)</li>\n<li>(3 comma negative 4)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>The area above the boundary is shaded.</li>\n</ul></div></figure></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The shaded region shown represents the solutions to the inequality <math alttext=\"r y less than 60\"><mi>r</mi><mi>y</mi><mo>&#60;</mo><mn>60</mn></math>, where <math alttext=\"r\"><mi>r</mi>\n</math> is a constant. What is the value of <math alttext=\"r\"><mi>r</mi>\n</math>?</p>",
